  "calendarMarkdown": "In the case of an external site,it may or may not meet accessibility guidelines.\n\n[![ANA](https://www.ana.co.jp/common-layout/images/logo.gif)](https://www.ana.co.jp/)\n\n![Inspiration of JAPAN](https://www.ana.co.jp/common-layout/images/logo_ioj.gif)\n\n# ANA International Award Calendar\n\nYou can see approximate availability of ANA International flight award in routes and dates.\n\n**Availability varies from hour to hour, so the result may be different from actual availability.**\n\n[![Redeem your miles and take your whole family on a trip.](https://www.ana.co.jp/amc/tokutencal/image/hd_im_en.jpg)](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/local/amc/promo/tokuten_family/)\n\n## Please select destination , Zone, and class.\n\n### Zone SelectYour destination from Zone1 (Japan)\n\nPlease SelectZone2 South Korea · Russia 1Zone3 Asia 1Zone4 Asia 2Zone5 HawaiiZone6 North AmericaZone7 Europe · Russia 2Zone10 Oceania · Micronesia\n\n[Check Zone detail.![New Window](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/image/icon_blank_mw1712.png)](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/asw_common/amc/reference/tukau/kokusai.html#step1)\n\n### Class Select\n\nEconomyPremium EconomyBusinessFirst\n\n### ANA International flights\n\n|     |     |     |     |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| ![](https://www.ana.co.jp/amc/tokutencal/image/icon_3.png): | Wide open | ![](https://www.ana.co.jp/amc/tokutencal/image/icon_1.png): | Tight · Waitlisted |\n| ![](https://www.ana.co.jp/amc/tokutencal/image/icon_2.png): | Open | ![](https://www.ana.co.jp/amc/tokutencal/image/icon_0.png): | Unavailable Periods |\n| ![](https://www.ana.co.jp/amc/tokutencal/image/icon_4.png): | Please check the seat availability<br>duaring canpaign period |\n\nCheck the latest availability(from 355 days before the boarding) at [Award reservation![New Window](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/image/icon_blank_mw1712.png)](https://aswbe-i.ana.co.jp/international_asw/pages/award/search/roundtrip/award_search_roundtrip_input.xhtml?CONNECTION_KIND=JPN&LANG=en)\n\n| Destination |\n| --- |\n\n| Destination |\n| --- |\n\n| Destination |\n\n| Destination |\n| --- |\n\nPlease select Zone and class.\n\nLoading...\n\nThere is no data that corresponds to your conditions.\n\nPlease check the actual availability with [Award reservation.![New Window](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/image/icon_blank_mw1712.png)](https://aswbe-i.ana.co.jp/international_asw/pages/award/search/roundtrip/award_search_roundtrip_input.xhtml?CONNECTION_KIND=JPN&LANG=en)\n\n[Click here for the chart of required miles and other usage conditions](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/asw_common/amc/reference/tukau/kokusai.html#zone1)\n\n### Notes\n\n- **Please select the boarding date for both outbound and inbound to check the availability.**\n- This availability is for reference only based on the availability on last night. Real availability varies from hour to hour. Please check the latest availability by making a reservation.\n- You can apply from 9:00 a.m. (Japan time) of 355 days before your boarding day (not including the date of departure) until 96 hours before departure. However, reservations are taken after the start of the application for the entire itinerary.\n- The required number of miles differs according to the point of departure and destination zones, season, and boarding class. Please see [usage of conditions of ANA International flight award.![New Window](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/image/icon_blank_mw1712.png)](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/asw_common/amc/reference/tukau/kokusai.html)\n- The number of seats available for flight awards is also limited (depending on the flight, no seats may be made available at the start of the reservation period). In some cases, you may be unable to book using flight awards.\n- When there are multiple flights for a same sector, availability is displayed based on the total number of available seat.\n- If you wish to check seat availability for Partner flights, please proceed to [Award reservation.![New Window](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/image/icon_blank_mw1712.png)](https://aswbe-i.ana.co.jp/international_asw/pages/award/search/roundtrip/award_search_roundtrip_input.xhtml?CONNECTION_KIND=JPN&LANG=en)\n\n[Back to Top](https://cam.ana.co.jp/psz/tokutencal/form_e.jsp?CONNECTION_KIND=LAX&LANG=en#PAGETOP)\n\n[Contact Us](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/local/common/contact/)\n\n![](https://www.ana.co.jp/common-layout/images/icon_blank_WHT.png)In the case of an external site,it may or may not meet accessibility guidelines.\n\n- [Privacy Policy](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/local/common/aboutana/legal/)\n- [Terms and Conditions](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/local/common/terms/)\n- [Accessibility](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/local/common/user_env/)\n- [Sitemap](https://www.ana.co.jp/wws/japan/e/local/common/sitemap/index02_m.html)\n\n[![A STAR ALLIANCE MEMBER](https://www.ana.co.jp/common-layout/images/logo_star_alliance.gif)](http://www.staralliance.com/en/)\n\nCopyright©ANA"
